</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_139" id="69r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Fridrich Styeber,
                            <expan>dechant<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat furgelegt Sanwel
                        von Swarczach, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> jude, wie daz ir von
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Albrechts vom Eglofstein czu Mülhausen
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> panbrief über den
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> juden hergesant und den
                                <expan>panne<ex>n</ex></expan> habt lassen und im vormals ümb
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sach khein ladbrief
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey; und also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Molitor, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, in den pfarrhof hie czu sant Sebolt
                        geschickt und an dem <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> und den priestern allen
                        darynne erfaren lassen, ob in dhein ladbrief darümb geantwurtt sey worden,
                        und die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz in <expan>khein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sey <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, das uns fremde nymt, daz man die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> pannen sol, ee sie geladen werden.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, <add>daz</add> ir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> pan <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> abtun und ez dabey
                            <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen wöllet, als das von
                                <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
